093170875536251e-14, \"text\": \"Mumbai\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mumbai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mumbai\"}, {\"begin\": 248, \"end\": 257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangalore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6765162353675913e-23, \"text\": \"Bengaluru\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangalore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangalore\"}, {\"begin\": 305, \"end\": 310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999999999881766, \"rank\": 1.1732534651740146e-11, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Recently, India won its first medal at the prestigious event.Manu Bhakerwon the bronze medal in the Women's 10-metre Air Pistol final on Sunday.\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 349, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999999999881766, \"rank\": 1.1732534651740146e-11, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She scripted history and became the first Indian woman to win an Olympic medal in shooting.\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 526, \"end\": 532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_India\", \"score\": 0.9999999992164703, \"rank\": 5.741117962680542e-10, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her win has left every Indian beaming with pride.\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 599, \"end\": 605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_India\", \"score\": 0.9999999992164703, \"rank\": 5.741117962680542e-10, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bollywood celebrities like Deepika Padukone and Alia Bhatt among others took to their social media to congratulate Bhaker on her victory.\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 674, \"end\": 684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alia_Bhatt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alia Bhatt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alia_Bhatt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alia_Bhatt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taking to her Instagram Stories,Deepika Padukoneshared a picture of Manu Bhaker.\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 779, \"end\": 796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Instagram Stories\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 833, \"end\": 844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manu_Bhaker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Manu Bhaker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manu_Bhaker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manu_Bhaker\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kareena Kapoor congratulated her by sharing her picture as well.\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 910, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 846, \"end\": 860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kareena_Kapoor\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kareena Kapoor\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kareena_Kapoor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kareena_Kapoor\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Along with the picture, she wrote, \\\"First win is home!\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 965, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Congratulations @bhakermanu, you have made all of us sooo proud!!.\\\"\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1033, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alia Bhatt also congratulated her and wrote, \\\"Our first medal is here!\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1034, \"end\": 1044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alia_Bhatt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alia Bhatt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alia_Bhatt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alia_Bhatt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Congratulations on this amazing achievement!\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"@bhakermanu #Paris2024 @weareteamindia.\\\"\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1190, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Take a look at their posts forManu Bhakerhere.\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1238, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally,Rajkummar Raoalso congratulated Bhaker and wrote, \\\"Congratulations @bhakermanu We all are so proud of you.\\\"\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Varun Dhawan shared a picture of Bhaker posing with the medal in Paris.Anushka Sharmawrote, \\\"Shooting for the stars and creating history!!!\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1361, \"end\": 1373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Varun_Dhawan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Varun Dhawan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Varun_Dhawan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Varun_Dhawan\"}, {\"begin\": 1361, \"end\": 1373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Varun_Dhawan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Varun Dhawan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Varun_Dhawan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Varun_Dhawan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Congratulations @bhakermanu you have made us all proud.\\\"\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1557, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Take a look at their Stories here.\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1593, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"22-year-old Bhaker achieved a remarkable score of 221.7, clinching third place.\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1674, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This win is particularly noteworthy as she is the first Indian woman to reach an individual shooting final in twenty years, a feat last achieved by Suma Shirur in 2004.\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1843, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1731, \"end\": 1737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_India\", \"score\": 0.9999999992164703, \"rank\": 5.741117962680542e-10, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_India\"}, {\"begin\": 1823, \"end\": 1834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Suma_Shirur\", \"score\": 0.999999891097565, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Suma Shirur\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Suma_Shirur\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Suma_Shirur\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the Women's 10 Metre Air Pistol final, South Korea's Ye Jin set a new Olympic record with a score of 243.2 to win gold, while her fellow countrywoman Kim Yeji secured silver with 241.3 points.\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 2039, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1886, \"end\": 1897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9999999926435521, \"rank\": 4.741018520713463e-09, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 1900, \"end\": 1902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.